products.name: Samsung Galaxy S21 Ultra
products.description: Samsung Galaxy S21 Ultra is an Android-based smartphone that is part of the Samsung Galaxy S series. It features a 6.8-inch Dynamic AMOLED display, 108MP primary sensor, 40MP front camera, 5000mAh battery, up to 16GB of RAM, and Exynos 2100 chipset.

products.name: Apple Airpods Max 2
products.description: AirPods Max are wireless Bluetooth over-ear headphones designed by Apple, and released on December 15, 2020. They are Apple's highest-end option in the AirPods lineup, sold alongside the base model AirPods and mid-range AirPods Pro.
